00:00:07.980 --> 00:00:11.820 align:middle line:84%
>> When we cultivate it and
we bring it into our conscious

00:00:11.820 --> 00:00:16.050 align:middle line:84%
awareness, then it provides a
lot of magical transformation

00:00:16.050 --> 00:00:17.880 align:middle line:90%
and healing for our lives.

